GET http://localhost:5000/?text=Robbie+Coltrane%2C+a+long-time+Scottish-born+comic+and+actor+-+best+known+for+his+popular+roles+in+the+British+crime+series+Cracker+and+the+Harry+Potter+movie+franchise+-+has+passed%2C+his+agency+WME+just+confirmed+to+The+Hollywood+Reporter.%0A%0AHe+was+72+years+old.%0A%0AThe+cause+of+death+wasn%27t+immediately+disclosed.%0A%0A%22For+me+personally+I+shall+remember+him+as+an+abidingly+loyal+client%2C%22+the+star%27s+agent%2C+Belinda+Wright%2C+said+in+statement+to+the+Press+Association.%0A%0A%22As+well+as+being+a+wonderful+actor%2C+he+was+forensically+intelligent%2C+brilliantly+witty+and+after+40+years+of+being+proud+to+be+called+his+agent%2C+I+shall+miss+him.%22%0A%0AColtrane+won+three+consecutive+British+Academy+of+Film+and+Television+Arts+%28BAFTA%29+awards+for+Best+Actor+due+to+his+work+on+Cracker%2C+on+which+he+portrayed+a+foul-mouthed%2C+hard-drinking%2C+gambling-addicted+forensic+psychologist.%0A%0AHe+also+appeared+as+the+villain+Valentin+Zukovsky+in+two+James+Bond+films%2C+GoldenEye+and+The+World+Is+Not+Enough.%0AFor+his+turn+as+Hagrid%2C+the+adorable+groundskeeper+at+Hogwarts%2C+Coltrane+appeared+in+every+Harry+Potter+movie.%0A%0ADuring+his+appearance+on+Harry+Potter+20th+Anniversary%3A+Return+to+Hogwarts%2C+the+actor+grew+emotional+when+talking+about+what+Hagrid+meant+to+him.%0A%0A%22It%27s+the+end+of+an+era.+Ten+years+of+my+life.+My+children+have+grown+up+during+it%2C%22+he+said+at+the+event.%0A%0A%22The+legacy+of+the+movies+is+that+my+children%27s+generation+will+show+them+to+their+children+...%22%0A%22So+you+could+be+watching+it+in+50+year%27s+time%2C+easily+...+I%27ll+not+be+here%2C+sadly+%E2%80%A6+but+Hagrid+will%2C+yes.%22%0A%0AIn+2019%2C+Coltrane+reprised+his+role+as+Hagrid+in+the+fantasy+short+film+Hagrid%27s+Magical+Creatures+Motorbike+Adventure.%0A%0AElsewhere%2C+the+late+star+penned+an+autobiography%2C+Coltrane+in+a+Cadillac%2C+and+also+starred+in+a+teelvision+series+of+the+same+name+in+1993%E2%80%A6+where+he+drove+across+America+from+Los+Angeles+to+New+York+City+in+a+classic+1951+Cadillac+vehicle.%0A%0AIn+the+1980s%2C+Coltrane+appeared+in+a+short-lived+sketch+series+called+%22Alfresco%22+alongside+major+names+Hugh+Laurie%2C+Stephen+Fry+and+Emma+Thompson.%0A%0AOn+Friday%2C+Fry+honored+his+former+co-star+in+a+statement+shared+to+Twitter.%0A%0A%22I+first+met+Robbie+Coltrane+almost+exactly+40+years+ago.+I+was+awe%2Fterror%2Flove+struck+all+at+the+same+time.+Such+depth%2C+power+%26+talent%3A+funny+enough+to+cause+helpless+hiccups+%26+honking+as+we+made+our+first+TV+show%2C+Alfresco.%0A%0A%22Farewell%2C+old+fellow.%22


